  "texts": [
    "We divided the wheat genomes into 50-kb windows and assigned each window to an Ae.",
    "tauschii subpopulation based on identity-by-state 13.",
    "We observed that all four Ae.",
    "tauschii L2 subpopulations contributed genomic segments to the bread wheat D genome (Supplementary Table 19).",
    "Consistent with previous reports 5, the largest proportion of the wheat D genome (45.6-51.3%) originated from subpopulation L2E-1, which is mainly found in the southwestern Caspian Sea region."
  ],
